column2: SELECT m.ra, m.dec, p.objid, p.g, p.r,  g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_#_flux into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.galaxyData AS m   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n   JOIN photoObj AS p ON p.objid = n.objid   JOIN GalSpecLine AS g ON g.specobjid = p.specobjid   JOIN galSpecInfo AS i ON i.specobjid = g.specobjid   JOIN specObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid AND s.Class= &&& AND g.h_alpha_flux > # AND g.nii_#_flux > # AND g.h_alpha_flux_err < g.h_alpha_flux AND g.nii_#_flux_err < g.nii_#_flux AND i.subclass != &&&
